{
  "texts": [
    "MethodsThe RISE, an innovative retrieval augmentation framework, comprises four steps: Rewriting Query, Information Retrieval, Summarization, and Execution.",
    "Using a set of 43 common diabetes-related questions, we evaluated three base LLMs (GPT-4, Anthropic Claude 2, Google Bard) and their RISEenhanced versions.",
    "Assessments were conducted by clinicians for accuracy and comprehensiveness, and by patients for understandability.",
    "ResultsThe integration of RISE significantly improved the accuracy and comprehensiveness of responses from all three based LLMs.On average, the percentage of accurate responses increased by 12% (122 -107/129) with RISE.",
    "Specifically, the rates of accurate responses increased by 7% (42 -39/43) for GPT-4, 19% (39 -31/43) for Claude 2, and 9% (41 -37/43) for Google Bard."
  ]
}